Class ReduceDecimalsRule.FloorExpander

  • java.lang.Object

  • Enclosing class:
    ReduceDecimalsRule

    private class ReduceDecimalsRule.FloorExpander
extends ReduceDecimalsRule.RexExpander
    Expander that rewrites floor(decimal) expressions: 
     if (value < 0)
     (value - 0.99...) / (10^scale)
 else
     value / (10 ^ scale)
